 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Field Service Engineer (Entry Level) Smart Vision Works Orem, UT Full-time Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Overview 
 
We are looking for a detail-oriented, tech-savvy, customer-centric, get-your-hands-dirty Field Engineer to support our rapidly growing high-tech company. As a leader in AI and machine learning vision, the demand for our systems and services has exploded across multiple industries requiring us to expand our Field Engineering team. This role is critical to our success as it directly interfaces with the end customer and manages system installations from planning all the way to support, ensuring a positive implementation experience. 
Responsibilities 
 
 Troubleshoot and resolve complex mechanical and electrical issues in production facilities both remotely and in person. 
 Orchestrate and execute new system installations 
 Connect to and troubleshoot customer networks 
 Configure and calibrate devices in the field. 
 Provide detailed training to customer management and operators 
 Document solutions to known issues 
 Manage project status and activity reporting to customers and management. 
 Travel to customer sites 50-75% of the time. 
 
 
Skills Required 
 
 Outstanding customer service skills 
 Excellent analytical, interpersonal, communication skills 
 Able to read electrical/mechanical drawings 
 Able to analyze complex issues and alternate solutions 
 Working knowledge of test equipment (oscilloscopes, multimeters) 
 Able to lift and carry 25lb. 
 
 
Experience Preferred 
 
 Hands-on electrical experience 
 Experience with heavy machinery and systems 
 Experience working in a production or manufacturing environment a plus 
 Exposure to hardware/software integration 
 
 
Desired Skills 
 
 Basic understanding of computer networking 
 CAD or other drawing software experience a plus 
 Knowledge and understanding of Linux software a plus 
 Experience working with robotics a plus 
 Exposure to machine vision technology a plus Smart Vision Works 30+ days ago original job If you require alternative methods of application or screening, you must approach the employer directly to request this as Indeed is not responsible for the employer's application process. Report job Apply Now Apply Now Save this job Save this job Field Service Engineer jobs in Orem, UT Jobs at Smart Vision Works in Orem, UT Field Service Engineer salaries in Orem, UT Company Info Follow Get job updates from Smart Vision Works Let employers find you Thousands of employers search for candidates on Indeed Upload your resume 
 
